lead_paragraph: A cache of Hillary Clinton emails expected to be made public soon contains no support for Republican accusations that Clinton was involved in efforts to downplay the role of Islamic militants in the deadly 2012 attacks on U.S. installations in Benghazi, Libya, people familiar with the emails said.

headline.main: Hillary Clinton's Benghazi Emails Contain Few Revelations: Sources
headline.print_headline: Hillary Clinton's Benghazi Emails Contain Few Revelations: Sources
